profile:
Welcome to Budget Blinds of Kamloops. We have been servicing the Okanagan area for 15 years. Offering home town service and big box prices. We offer FREE QUOTES.  We're your local experts and are proud to be backed by the #1 provider of custom window coverings in North America that has provided design-driven solutions for over 25 years. With the highest levels of customer satisfaction, you'll have the peace of mind and security that comes with choosing the proven leader. We’ll get to know you and your unique style so we can deliver the perfect solution for your home. 

***

Explore what Beautiful can do for your windows. Contact us today to schedule your appointment. We’re looking forward to working with you.
